        <div class="body">
            <p>The problem here was being caused by the while-statement on line 472 of Zend_Tool_Framework_Client_Console_ArgumentParser class</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
while (($wordOnTop = array_shift($this-&gt;_argumentsWorking))){
    //...
}
</code></pre>

<p>There was the possibility of $wordOnTop being == 0 which would break out the while loop
i.e zf create action actionName 0 moduleName</p>

<p>Just change to seems to fix things</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
while (($wordOnTop = array_shift($this-&gt;_argumentsWorking)) !== false){
    //...
}
</code></pre>

<p>I've attached a patch</p>

